Sentencas: The nanocrystalline BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 (BCZY) thin films have been deposited on alumina substrate by simple and economic spray pyrolysis technique.
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The spray deposited films were annealed at different temperatures and were characterized by different physio-chemical techniques.
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The XRD studies revealed orthorhombic structured BCZY thin films with little shift in 2 theta compared to BCY.
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The crystallite size and grain size were observed to enhance with annealing temperature.
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The grain growth was completed by 1000 degrees C and compact structure was obtained at 1100 degrees C. Evolution of the surface microstructure and roughness of the BCY and BCZY thin films is done using AFM.
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Raman spectra of BCZY and BCY exhibits pronounced characteristic band at 359 and 353.25 cm(-1) respectively.
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The proton conductivity of BCZY thin film in moist atmosphere was 0.83 x 10(-3) S cm(-1) at 400 degrees C. (C) 2014
Titulo: Proton conducting BaCe0.7Zr0.1Y0.2O2.9 thin films by spray deposition for solid oxide fuel cell
